name: precisionFDA
description: precisionFDA is a cloud based platform that provides an environment where the community can test, pilot, and benchmark new approaches to validating their next-generation sequencing (NGS) analysis pipelines. PrecisionFDA offers community members a secure and independent work area where, at their discretion, their bioinformatics tools or data can be kept private or shared with the precisionFDA participants.
